WEBVTT - Close Eye Founder Story

scene-0-line-0
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.042
Hi. I'm Krishna.

scene-0-line-1
00:00:01.442 --> 00:00:02.223
Not the Founder.

scene-0-line-2
00:00:02.623 --> 00:00:03.404
Not the CEO.

scene-0-line-3
00:00:03.804 --> 00:00:04.325
Just Krishna.

scene-1-line-0
00:00:06.325 --> 00:00:08.669
Thank you for taking a few minutes to listen.

scene-1-line-1
00:00:09.069 --> 00:00:10.892
Before I tell you about Close Eye,

scene-1-line-2
00:00:11.292 --> 00:00:14.417
I want to tell you about one day that changed my life.

scene-2-line-0
00:00:16.417 --> 00:00:18.760
A little while ago, on the 16th of June,

scene-2-line-1
00:00:19.160 --> 00:00:20.202
my daughter was born.

scene-2-line-2
00:00:20.602 --> 00:00:22.685
It was the happiest day of my life.

scene-2-line-3
00:00:23.085 --> 00:00:25.429
But somehow, it was also one of the loneliest.

scene-3-line-0
00:00:27.429 --> 00:00:30.033
In that room, there were only a few of us.

scene-3-line-1
00:00:30.433 --> 00:00:31.735
My wife. Our new baby.

scene-3-line-2
00:00:32.135 --> 00:00:34.1000
My sister-in-law, who stayed with us the whole time.

scene-3-line-3
00:00:35.400 --> 00:00:36.181
And my parents.

scene-3-line-4
00:00:36.581 --> 00:00:38.404
Everyone else I loved was far away.

scene-4-line-0
00:00:40.404 --> 00:00:42.227
There was no crowd outside the door.

scene-4-line-1
00:00:42.627 --> 00:00:44.190
No phone ringing again and again.

scene-4-line-2
00:00:44.590 --> 00:00:46.412
For a few minutes, everything was quiet.

scene-4-line-3
00:00:46.812 --> 00:00:48.896
I held my daughter for the first time.

scene-4-line-4
00:00:49.296 --> 00:00:51.119
I wanted to tell the whole world.

scene-4-line-5
00:00:51.519 --> 00:00:54.123
But I realised — I had almost no one to call.

scene-5-line-0
00:00:56.123 --> 00:00:57.946
Then one thought came to my mind.

scene-5-line-1
00:00:58.346 --> 00:00:59.908
The same thought every parent has:

scene-5-line-2
00:01:00.308 --> 00:01:02.912
“What will happen to her if something happens to me?”

scene-5-line-3
00:01:03.312 --> 00:01:05.656
I didn't want someone to replace her family.

scene-5-line-4
00:01:06.056 --> 00:01:08.400
I wanted something that could make her family stronger.

scene-5-line-5
00:01:08.800 --> 00:01:11.404
Someone she can trust — when we can't be there.

scene-6-line-0
00:01:13.404 --> 00:01:14.446
Then I understood something.

scene-6-line-1
00:01:14.846 --> 00:01:16.669
Millions of families feel this same way.

scene-6-line-2
00:01:17.069 --> 00:01:17.850
Parents getting older.

scene-6-line-3
00:01:18.250 --> 00:01:20.073
Children living far away, in other countries.

scene-6-line-4
00:01:20.473 --> 00:01:21.254
Grandparents missing birthdays.

scene-6-line-5
00:01:21.654 --> 00:01:23.738
Every night, someone is thinking: “Are they okay?”

scene-7-line-0
00:01:25.738 --> 00:01:28.342
That was the moment Close Eye became real for me.

scene-7-line-1
00:01:28.742 --> 00:01:30.565
It was no longer just an idea.

scene-7-line-2
00:01:30.965 --> 00:01:32.006
It became my responsibility.

scene-7-line-3
00:01:32.406 --> 00:01:35.531
So that no family has to face life's big moments alone.

scene-8-line-0
00:01:37.531 --> 00:01:39.875
We don't replace families. We make them stronger.

scene-8-line-1
00:01:40.275 --> 00:01:42.098
We don't replace sons and daughters.

scene-8-line-2
00:01:42.498 --> 00:01:44.842
We help them stay close, even from far away.

scene-8-line-3
00:01:45.242 --> 00:01:47.065
We help families care for each other —

scene-8-line-4
00:01:47.465 --> 00:01:48.767
with love, respect, and trust.

scene-9-line-0
00:01:50.767 --> 00:01:51.808
Every visit. Every message.

scene-9-line-1
00:01:52.208 --> 00:01:53.250
Every companion. Every call.

scene-9-line-2
00:01:53.650 --> 00:01:54.952
Is a family trusting us.

scene-9-line-3
00:01:55.352 --> 00:01:56.654
When you join Close Eye,

scene-9-line-4
00:01:57.054 --> 00:01:58.877
you are not just joining a company.

scene-9-line-5
00:01:59.277 --> 00:02:01.100
You are becoming someone's trusted presence.

scene-10-line-0
00:02:03.100 --> 00:02:04.923
That day, I made one more promise.

scene-10-line-1
00:02:05.323 --> 00:02:07.667
Close Eye should not grow only for its founders.

scene-10-line-2
00:02:08.067 --> 00:02:10.410
It should grow with the people who build it.

scene-10-line-3
00:02:10.810 --> 00:02:12.894
Work like an owner. Be honest. Protect trust.

scene-10-line-4
00:02:13.294 --> 00:02:15.117
Because trust is not built by software.

scene-10-line-5
00:02:15.517 --> 00:02:16.819
Trust is built by people.

scene-11-line-0
00:02:18.819 --> 00:02:20.642
Every year, on the 16th of June,

scene-11-line-1
00:02:21.042 --> 00:02:22.344
we will celebrate Family Day.

scene-11-line-2
00:02:22.744 --> 00:02:24.306
To remember why Close Eye exists —

scene-11-line-3
00:02:24.706 --> 00:02:26.529
that every request is a real family,

scene-11-line-4
00:02:26.929 --> 00:02:29.794
and that no app can replace a real person being there.

scene-12-line-0
00:02:31.794 --> 00:02:34.138
One day, I hope you will meet my daughter.

scene-12-line-1
00:02:34.538 --> 00:02:36.100
Not because she is our brand.

scene-12-line-2
00:02:36.500 --> 00:02:38.844
But because she reminds us why this work matters.

scene-12-line-3
00:02:39.244 --> 00:02:40.285
Every child deserves grandparents.

scene-12-line-4
00:02:40.685 --> 00:02:42.508
Every grandparent deserves a child's laughter.

scene-12-line-5
00:02:42.908 --> 00:02:44.731
And every family deserves to stay close,

scene-12-line-6
00:02:45.131 --> 00:02:46.433
however far apart they live.

scene-13-line-0
00:02:48.433 --> 00:02:49.475
Please remember one thing.

scene-13-line-1
00:02:49.875 --> 00:02:50.917
Every notification. Every call.

scene-13-line-2
00:02:51.317 --> 00:02:52.358
Every visit. Every decision.

scene-13-line-3
00:02:52.758 --> 00:02:54.060
Is about someone's family.

scene-13-line-4
00:02:54.460 --> 00:02:56.804
Because of your work, someone will sleep peacefully tonight.

scene-13-line-5
00:02:57.204 --> 00:02:58.246
This is our responsibility.

scene-13-line-6
00:02:58.646 --> 00:02:59.688
This is our honour.

scene-13-line-7
00:03:00.088 --> 00:03:01.129
Welcome to Close Eye.

scene-13-line-8
00:03:01.529 --> 00:03:03.352
Thank you for believing in this mission.

scene-13-line-9
00:03:03.752 --> 00:03:05.835
Thank you for becoming part of Close Eye.

scene-13-line-10
00:03:06.235 --> 00:03:09.100
Together, let's build the world's most trusted presence network.
